I did the cover art for NICOLA BERRY books 1-3 by Liane Moriarty! These are great sci fi/fantasy chapter books for kids, in stores now! Im very proud of these covers! 😄

I've started a new project drawing snapshots of my garden, called "devotionals" for the daily devotion i give to all my plants as they grow. It is so nice to work with real media again. I post each new one to my Story, so keep an eye out.

I have a Patreon! Patreon.com/rebeccamock $3/month patrons will get to see exclusive behind-the-scenes art like this for my current book in progress (written by @despairlarson ) It’s a relief to be able to sketch parts of this book in Procreate so I’m not chained to my desk 😂
